snippet.title: Stick it to the Stickman | Devolver Holiday Special Spotlight
snippet.description:
Stickedin is the leading job site for stick people. Are you tired of dead end jobs? At Stickedin, you can pursue your dream career.

Try the Stick it to the Stickman demo at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2085540/Stick_It_to_the_Stickman/

Obtain your next opportunity at https://www.stickittothestickman.com/
